"title": "7125: elect, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7125",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those chosen by God, entirely of his grace, for the special privilege of experiencing salvation.</p>\n<h2>Israel as the elect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:4-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:4–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:6\">PSA 105:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:43\">PSA 105:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:4\">PSA 135:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:9\">ISA 41:8–41:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:10\">ISA 43:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:1-Isa44:2\">ISA 44:1–44:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:4\">ISA 45:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:2\">AMO 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:1-Rom11:18\">ROM 11:1–11:18</a></p>\n<h2>The church as the elect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4-Eph1:13\">EPH 1:4–1:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1-1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:1–1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:4-John10:5\">JHN 10:4–10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:4-1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:132\">1PE 5:132</a>JN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:13\">2JN 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Individuals chosen by God as his elect</h2>\n<h3>Abraham</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:18-Gen18:19\">GEN 18:18–18:19</a></p>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:23\">PSA 106:23</a></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:16\">1KI 8:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:3-Ps89:4\">PSA 89:3–89:4</a></p>\n<h3>Rufus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:13\">ROM 16:13</a></p>\n<h2>God's elect enjoy his presence and favour</h2>\n<h3>The elect are asssured of the presence of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5-Heb13:6\">HEB 13:5–13:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:1-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:1–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:6\">PSA 23:1–23:6</a></p>\n<h3>The elect are assured of the protection of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:22\">MAT 24:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:20\">MRK 13:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:33–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a></p>\n<h3>The elect are assured of a place in the world to come</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:26–13:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:30–24:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17-Isa65:25\">ISA 65:17–65:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1-John14:3\">JHN 14:1–14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>The elect are assured of justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:7-Luke18:8\">LUK 18:7–18:8</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Responsibilities of the elect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:17\">COL 3:12–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:1-Deut14:2\">DEU 14:1–14:2</a></p>",
